THE OPEN CHAMPIONSHIP
July 18, 2015
Hideki Matsuyama
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







Q. How much pressure do you feel to try and win?HIDEKI MATSUYAMA: Really don't even think about it.Q. Don't even think about it, so there's no pressure, you just go out and play?HIDEKI MATSUYAMA: If you look around at all these Japanese media here, of course I feel some pressure.  All I can do is just do my best and hope for the best.Q. Are you ready to win your first major?HIDEKI MATSUYAMA: I'd like to be able to say so.


END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT